to a buried body found at a thrift store”.

00:00:42.300 --> 00:00:46.733
The truth is under and underneath
it says the body lies at...

00:00:46.733 --> 00:00:48.733
And there's a series of coordinates.

00:00:48.733 --> 00:00:50.000
It's exactly what it says.

00:00:50.000 --> 00:00:53.900
This guy was at a thrift store, found
random coordinates, decided to end up posting

00:00:53.900 --> 00:00:57.033
it to the Internet, and supposedly
came across a dead body.

00:00:57.033 --> 00:01:01.500
Whang covers these internet mysteries that, again,

00:01:01.500 --> 00:01:04.633
