00:05:54.000 --> 00:05:56.500
True crime. Excellent. True crime.

00:05:56.500 --> 00:05:57.533
This is a fun one. All right.

00:05:57.533 --> 00:06:01.666
JCS.  Son spends $275,000 of Dad's virtual...

00:06:01.766 --> 00:06:03.333
of Dad’s money on virtual girlfriend.

00:06:03.333 --> 00:06:04.500
Yes, not his virtual money.

00:06:04.500 --> 00:06:05.400
It was real money.

00:06:05.400 --> 00:06:06.900
Grant Amado was sentenced

00:06:06.900 --> 00:06:07.900
to life in prison

00:06:07.900 --> 00:06:09.566
without the possibility of parole.

00:06:09.566 --> 00:06:11.400
JCS is a channel

00:06:11.400 --> 00:06:12.600
that I'm enamored with,

00:06:12.600 --> 00:06:14.133
as are a lot of other people.

00:06:14.133 --> 00:06:15.000
They've climbed

00:06:15.000 --> 00:06:18.233
the subscriber ranks faster than I think

00:06:18.233 --> 00:06:18.966
any other channel

00:06:18.966 --> 00:06:20.000
I've seen on the platform.

00:06:20.000 --> 00:06:21.200
And rightfully so.

00:06:21.200 --> 00:06:24.633
JCS takes interrogations

00:06:24.700 --> 00:06:26.666
that have happened in criminal cases,

00:06:26.666 --> 00:06:28.300
most often murder cases,

00:06:28.300 --> 00:06:30.500
and dissects them from a psychology

00:06:30.500 --> 00:06:31.133
point of view.

00:06:31.133 --> 00:06:31.800
For example,

00:06:31.800 --> 00:06:33.400
a person may simply shift

00:06:33.400 --> 00:06:35.733
their weight or cross their arms or

00:06:35.733 --> 00:06:36.900
hold themself in such a way

00:06:36.900 --> 00:06:38.433
that you wouldn't think anything of it.

00:06:38.433 --> 00:06:39.933
But then, as JCS points out,

00:06:39.933 --> 00:06:42.000
they have some strategy going on, or perhaps

00:06:42.000 --> 00:06:43.900
it's just some exhibition of stress

00:06:43.900 --> 00:06:44.633
or what have you.

00:06:44.633 --> 00:06:46.700
And another detail I like about JCS

00:06:46.700 --> 00:06:49.633
is the way they're able to give respect

00:06:49.633 --> 00:06:50.733
to a lot of the victims

00:06:50.733 --> 00:06:51.700
or a lot of these cases.

00:06:51.700 --> 00:06:52.233
And it's something

00:06:52.233 --> 00:06:53.966
that I ask myself a lot like

00:06:53.966 --> 00:06:55.466
how do I be respectful

00:06:55.466 --> 00:06:56.400
while also talking

00:06:56.400 --> 00:06:57.533
about a sensitive issue?

00:06:57.533 --> 00:06:59.033
A lot of times I'll need to sit

00:06:59.033 --> 00:07:00.900
with a video topic for a while and think about it.

00:07:00.900 --> 00:07:01.466
For example,

00:07:01.466 --> 00:07:02.633
I recently

00:07:02.633 --> 00:07:05.766
made a video about the Yuba County five.

00:07:05.766 --> 00:07:07.300
Four of them were eventually found dead

00:07:07.300 --> 00:07:09.566
and one of them is still a missing persons to this day.

00:07:09.566 --> 00:07:11.800
And it has been the historic record

00:07:11.800 --> 00:07:12.566
for some time

00:07:12.566 --> 00:07:14.266
that the one who disappeared

00:07:14.266 --> 00:07:15.433
was the perpetrator.

00:07:15.433 --> 00:07:17.100
And I came to the conclusion with myself

00:07:17.100 --> 00:07:18.000
that I don't think he did it.

00:07:18.000 --> 00:07:19.133
I sat with myself a while

00:07:19.133 --> 00:07:20.300
before I recorded that video

00:07:20.300 --> 00:07:22.166
and thought, like, is this the interpretation

00:07:22.166 --> 00:07:22.866
I want to give out?

00:07:22.866 --> 00:07:25.300
I want to say about half a dozen video topics

00:07:25.300 --> 00:07:26.633
that I have got all the way

00:07:26.633 --> 00:07:27.900
to like ready to record.

00:07:27.900 --> 00:07:30.000
And then I stop myself because I get

00:07:30.000 --> 00:07:30.933
I get to that last stage.

00:07:30.933 --> 00:07:32.700
I'm like, I can't talk about this

00:07:32.700 --> 00:07:33.600
or I don't

00:07:33.600 --> 00:07:35.233
maybe I don't know the way to talk about it.

00:07:35.233 --> 00:07:36.266
And channels like JCS

00:07:36.266 --> 00:07:37.300
do a great job of that

00:07:37.300 --> 00:07:38.133
and are certainly something

00:07:38.133 --> 00:07:40.500
to aspire towards in that situation.

00:07:40.500 --> 00:07:41.466
With that out of the way,

00:07:41.466 --> 00:07:44.433
I guess we can move on to something else.

