“I watched four disturbing movies

00:07:57.333 --> 00:08:00.833
and only one didn't suck” from my boy, Mista GG

00:08:00.833 --> 00:08:02.400
If the disturbing aspect of this movie

00:08:02.400 --> 00:08:03.666
is supposed to be the quality,

00:08:03.666 --> 00:08:04.500
then it's spot on.

00:08:04.500 --> 00:08:05.866
What he's really good

00:08:05.866 --> 00:08:09.000
at is making scary things digestible,

00:08:09.000 --> 00:08:09.866
making them not scary.

00:08:09.866 --> 00:08:11.633
Which is what I do, I think.

00:08:11.633 --> 00:08:13.800
